name: A Mystery Dozen Lot of Handmade Cards
description:
For sale is a mystery dozen (12pcs) lot of handmade cards handcrafted by me and you will not get the repeated design.

	You will receive the following :
1) Happy Birthday (x6)
2) Thank You (x2)
3) Congratulations (x1)
4) Happy Anniversary (x1)
5) Love (x2)

	Each card is blank inside, comes with a matching colour envelope, measures 6” by 4”, and comes wrapped in a cellophane bag.

	A great collection of cards for your whole year needs!
